Necromancers
Necromancers are masters of death, undeath, and the powers of the
supernatural. They are extremely fragile physically, but have the
potential to deal a large amount of damage through both their variety of
~>spells<~ and their ~>followers<~. These powers flow through their
two ~>runes<~.

Topics of interest (use "nechelp <topic>"):

~>advancement<~, ~>Alarian<~, ~>equipment<~, ~>followers<~,
~>GuildHouse<~, ~>monitor<~, ~>runes<~, ~>spells<~, and ~>stats<~,

